p.k: Hey Pizza! / Gorilla / Girls' Night Out / You're Fired Beast Boy and Cyborg try their best to slow the pizza delivery boy so they can get free pizza. / Beast Boy takes over as Alpha male of the Titans when he is in Gorilla-mode and Robin has to figure out how to get back on top. / When the guys plan a guys night out Starfire drags Raven out on a wild adventure of their own. / Beast Boy gets fired from the team and the Wonder Twins take his place.
